reviews: Just fell apart half way through string replacement, nothing snapped, just fell apart.
Came with 2 microfiber clothes for drying and polishing, wipes work great, can not complain, I would recommend these to any one who wears glasses.

This device was $20, advertised as an "injection cleaning system" figured that lens cleaner would come out from the pads, it doesn't. Doesn't come with any cleaner, and really the 2 stupid pads is the same as taking your two fingers and using a cloth. Not even a better clean, still smudges no matter how many times I tried.

review_title: No temps above 70 AAA games on ultra
reviews: Keeps the system cool, it's huge, little trickier to install then other coolers, just because it's so big and has a unique mounting system.
Easy to install, works great, awesome.
Have a huge head, no hats fit right, except this one, plain, black hat, perfect.

Picture made it look like this one for on your head perfect, but this one leaves that awkward little extra bit of hat stick off the top of your head, I like the top of my head to hit the hat, it's like how some kids wear their hat above their ears so they have a bit sticking high up, it's just weird, fashionable I suppose.

It's also really tight, probably better if you're bald, if you have some hair, you'll get serious hat head.

review_title: Great case, inspect yours for damages
reviews:
TL:DR;

Great case for $129.99 CAD, mine had a dent in the front panel and had to wait 2 weeks.

----------------------------------------------------------

This case is great, great quality and cable management, have nothing bad to say about it, the tempered glass panel can be a little finicky because the screws and threads are so short.

The only reason I am giving 2 stars is because mine came with a nice dent in the top of the front panel, I am aware I probably could have sent it back and had it replaced, but when I ordered it originally the case said in stock with prime delivery, then they emailed me and said that it was on back order, waited 2 weeks and it finally showed up and I did not feel like waiting to build my computer for another 2 weeks.
Works great for Windows, would not show up for Linux.

review_title: Does not work at all, do not buy
reviews: Screw fell out of the back immediately as soon as I opened up the little bag, the connector is loose, doesn't function at all what so ever, can not tell if it's a dud or just false advertising. Do not buy it.

review_title: Key not swappable as advertised, MUST be cut.
reviews:
This key is not as advertised, in the description for this product, this is quoted

"Key case and uncut key blade only.Not electronic internals. Getblade cut by local locksmith/dealer or swap the blade with your original."

You can NOT swap the blade with your original, it is molded into the plastic, you may not just use the new shell of your key did not snap,nyou have to get the new one cut.

Fantastic, makes perfect spheres. Great for about 3 double cocktails before it melts. Only thing I would add to this is a tray/shelf so you can make more at a time! Because they must be on flat surface they take up a portion of my freezer.

review_title: Power supply fell apart 4 months into use.
reviews:
Worked great for the most part for a while, auto switch was great unless you were running 2 things at once, then it's better to manual switch.

Remote does not work, what so ever.

4 months into use, the end of the power supply fell apart while I was rearranging my desk, and then no longer powered the switch.

Was cheaper to buy a new one then replace the power cord unfortunately, went with another model as this one was kind of poorly made, was great while it worked though.

Feels cheap, but seems to get the job done just fine! Says it has 2 usb inputs, fails to mention that one of the two is your power source that is then plugged into your hosts usb. So effectively, it just gives you the 1 usb port you are losing.

review_title: easy install, just have ugly lifts on the sides
reviews: Edges no not adhere well, easy install, just have ugly lifts on the sides.
